A vintage 1950s propaganda poster style illustration featuring a determined factory worker in overalls carefully placing glowing geometric objects into a large industrial recycling machine with gears and conveyor belts. The scene has warm sepia tones with bold orange and teal accents. Steam rises from brass pipes while small mechanical cats watch from the shadows of the factory floor. The composition uses dramatic diagonal lines and weathered paper texture with slightly faded edges, evoking mid-century industrial optimism and the importance of proper resource management.
